Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate \Nalliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they were trapped along \Nwith the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The executives of the Donquixote \NFamily have been taken down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,one after another, after hard \Nbattles, by the Straw Hats,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and finally, there is only Doflamingo left!{\i0}
