Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bounce-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rhino Schneider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Culverin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Athlete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crappy attack like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Culverin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Massive Counterattack!\NDoflamingo's Awakening!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A rubber ball is...\N--...Overwhelming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go for it!\N--You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:32.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE PLATEAU - LOCATION OF THE ROYAL PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:32.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe how he changed.\NIs it really Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's overpowering the formidable Doflamingo!\NHe's amazingly strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's using Haki too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using Haki too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is.\NThey went to play somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the trouble to come see them!\NHow annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The captain of the first ship of the Blackbeard Pirates -\NJesus Burgess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was wondering where he went\Nafter the battle in the Colosseum but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I found him here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase them or wait...\NEither way, I won't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get what I wanna get for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's going after Luffy-kun \Nand the others as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he want?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:59.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE CORRIDA COLOSSEUM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Viola.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that remains is the decisive battle\Nbetween him and Luffy-kun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right, Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo is the only one remaining now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from their forces from the \Nrank of executive or above.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Luffy-{\i1}kun{\i0} takes down Doflamingo,\Nthe Birdcage that is slicing up the town will vanish
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Doflamingo Family falls apart.\NIs that what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?! Did they get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bad at directions so if we just follow you,\Nwe'll never get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, why don't you ride on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that weird vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Spring Sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanjuro called it over \Nfrom the King's Plateau!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:09:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate.\NNow, hurry up and get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me getting on this Stupid Sparrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Spring Sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like it but I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring Sparrow! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It finally got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the factory, Tontattas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:04.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SMILE FACTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta escape!\N{\i1}Super{\i0} hurry up and come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We completed the rescue of\Nour stranded friends in the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The factory is tilting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fraland!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the SMILE Factory \Nalone not getting cut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh yeah, it's the Sea Prism Stone!\N--Sea Prism Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the outer walls of the factory are\Nmade of Sea Prism Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it doesn't get cut by the strings\Nthat the Devil Fruit eater created.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to get pushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Franky!\N--Oh, Robot-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoroland! Topknot-land!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The center of the country is \Nin the direction you flew from!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna run, go straight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We aren't running!\NWe'll go stop the strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them?\NOh, I didn't even think about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Luffy settles this, we gotta buy time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the strings... But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:59.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE DOWNTOWN\NLUFFY VS. DOFLAMINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's controlling the expansion \Nand contraction of rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,as he wants, with the Color of Arms...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harmonizing the Armament and rubber, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take too much time, Fourth Gear will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you're using your abilities pretty well\Nbut it must be quite a burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, how many more \Nseconds can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Double...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strings, however, won't run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Culverin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off-White!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did the strings \Ncome out of the ground?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, fledgling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fruit abilities have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet another stage to \Nthem called "Awakening"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The buildings turned into strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability will awaken rarely and begin to \Naffect things other than its user's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Various things are turning into strings!\NIt doesn't look like the power of a Paramythia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that surrounds \Nyou turns into strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when your strength gives out,\Nmy body will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope this tires you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your Haki gives out,\NI'll give you the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get cut! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up or we'll get cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, stand up! The strings will cut you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me here and go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! I can't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't survive this anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I get up, I definitely \Ncan't run to the downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still patients in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't carry them all by ourselves! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son's missing! Didn't anybody see him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wearing a Kuma shirt!\NHe's five years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody! Did you see my son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's gonna die anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far we run, we're in the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll only get killed by Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the former king of \NDressrosa - Riku Doldo III.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is now, by the game\Nthat the current king Doflamingo started,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a giant Birdcage with no visible escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On top of that, that vicious Birdcage\Nkeeps shrinking, slicing up the town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell on this reality too suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your emotions can't even catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're just trying to save your own,\Nor somebody else's, life now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is not a dream!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nor a tragedy that has begun today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a decade,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have always lived in the \NBirdcage called Dressrosa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the reign of the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a decade, we have always been puppets\Nthat live under their manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is reality!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that will end soon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Donquixote Family\Nthat we thought nobody could match has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...almost been wiped out by the \Nhands of the tough warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who only happened to be here in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Family's executives are\Nalready taken down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Those executives have...\N--...Brought down, he means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only enemy there is left to beat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the current king of \NDressrosa - Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who is fighting him is\Nthe pirate - Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he is the man\Nwho will destroy the Birdcage for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel very impotent\Nbecause although I'm a former king,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all I can do is to stake this country's fate\Non some strange pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can't help crying out like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he wins or loses,\Nit'll only take several dozen minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, try to survive, \Nwhatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want any one of you to get crushed\Nby the constriction of the country!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you run out of breath!\NOr even if your leg breaks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just for several dozen minutes,\Ntry to survive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best even without any help!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.46,0:22:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's run, granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--As King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0} said...!\N--We'll run to the downtown without giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry the sick people!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take those beds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to survive until the battle ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy will take \Ndown Doflamingo for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:28.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With his awakened Devil Fruit \Nabilities, Doflamingo turns objects
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:30.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,in the town into strings and \Nlaunches a full-scale attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:32.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a desperate situation where there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:37.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,is nowhere to run,\Nand as the time limit for Fourth Gear closes in,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:40.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy initiates a deciding deadly charge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Luffy! An All-Out Leo Bazooka!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
